name: Marvellous Ultimate Appliance
body:
The team page for Team Admiral Dolphin from GovHack 2013.

# Team Members
* Frank Sainsbury – oracle of all things.
* Tim Nugent – immortal.
* Jon Manning – codes all the things.
* Nic Wittison – only eats bacon.
* Matthew D'Orazio – breaks all the things.
* Rex Smeal – draws all the things.
* Josh Deprez - equates.
* Eloise Macdonald-Meyer - farming usurer. 
* Paris Buttfield-Addison – not entirely sure.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
